{"tid":1457650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住，我又犯左關原之戰既散水錯誤","createTime":"2019-08-12T12:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T16:56:00.000Z","uid":64191,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0592efe0ad905de9b0b3790df9fc135de3e55339","tid":1457650,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:01:26.000Z","msg":"400年前我本來聯合一眾義士，要對付奸臣德川家康同埋一眾暴力既武鬥派，準備要響美濃一帶與其決戰。<br />\n<br />\n點知因為聽到後面既大津城有內鬼，京極高次條仆街叫人散水，仲搞我地西軍既後防線，我地就中計，分左小早川秀包、立花宗茂兩位主戰力散水，搞到關原主戰時人手唔夠<br />\n<br />\n更唔好提後來小早川秀秋、吉川廣家呢兩件臥底，原來係德川家康既鬼，搞到我地西軍兵敗，刑部、左近、宇喜多秀家、小西行長、惠瓊都相繼逝去，豐臣家落入奸臣之手<br />\n<br />\n而今日，我穿越至此，又犯左400年前既錯誤，叫義士散水，真係好對唔住各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愧對逝去既西軍英靈"},{"pid":"45121def356e3a66d869f902f8ab03ecb92cd125","tid":1457650,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:19.000Z","msg":"西軍諸位相當抱歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfc701168fd63deba3cef5a345dd0ac0e22cbe8","tid":1457650,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:09.000Z","msg":"你切腹la"},{"pid":"64d5f448c4cf2e78bb34957611c69458a36adcba","tid":1457650,"uid":288670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:46.000Z","msg":"唔死無用"},{"pid":"7bb532a83e1f04fda7072514e7784d6b6a858fd1","tid":1457650,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:04:48.000Z","msg":"抵比德川打柒你"},{"pid":"d8ad593dc5c44b760df764496c07a4f301499150","tid":1457650,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:05:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱叫人留嘅手足比人屌到變過街老鼠"},{"pid":"9c0acf13205d72f80b37495d234f656588efffca","tid":1457650,"uid":301152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:07:25.000Z","msg":"唔洗切腹<br />\n去跟敵人同歸於盡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06f388511ee98ebb8a6386a668da68e975100f4e","tid":1457650,"uid":143343,